song_lyrics: Sahajānandjī sukhrūp chho re, shobhā taṇā shaṇagār re;
Mohanvar dayā karī darshan āpajo re... ṭek
Pūrve kahyu’tu Uddhavne re, laīsh bījo avatār re... Mohanvar 1
Puruṣhottam tame pragaṭī re, karyā sahunā kāj re... Mohanvar 2
Sukh-sāgar Ghanshyāmjī re, bhaktonā sukh jahāj re... Mohanvar 3
Shrījī tame Bhakti Dharmathī re, bhū par dharyo avatār re... Mohanvar 4
Brahmānand kahe māre tam thakī re, antare sukh apār re... Mohanvar 5
title: Sahajānandjī sukhrūp chho re
